casebody.data:
McAuliffe, Appellant, v. Grant, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. January 8, 1892.) Appeal from trial term. Action by Cornelius W. McAuliffe against Hugh J. Grant.

Argued before Bookstaver, Bisohoff, and Pryor, JJ.

J. P. Kiernan, for appellant. Coehran <6 Clark, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
